---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="Catalyst Privacy Policy"
      description="Privacy Policy for Catalyst Chain Reaction."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Privacy Policy - Catalyst Chain Reaction</h1>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> February 7, 2026</p>

      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how Catalyst Chain Reaction handles information when
        you use the app.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Use</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Gameplay and progress data stored locally on your device.</li>
        <li>Advertising-related identifiers and usage signals via ad partners.</li>
        <li>Purchase status and entitlement data via RevenueCat and Apple for in-app purchases.</li>
        <li>Diagnostics/performance data provided by platform and SDK services.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How Information Is Used</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Operate game features (levels, lives, progression).</li>
        <li>Serve and measure ads.</li>
        <li>Process and restore the Remove Ads purchase.</li>
        <li>Improve reliability and performance.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Google AdMob (ads and ad measurement)</li>
        <li>RevenueCat (in-app purchase management)</li>
        <li>Apple App Store / StoreKit (purchase processing)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You can request app tracking permissions through iOS prompts.</li>
        <li>You can purchase Remove Ads to stop ads in the app.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:rltorres26@gmail.com">rltorres26@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
